    <string name="csv_import_how_to">How to import to iOS:</string>
    <string name="csv_instr_1">Export and save the CSV file to your device.</string>
    <string name="csv_instr_2">Move the file to your iPhone or a Mac via iCloud, Email, or AirDrop.</string>
    <string name="csv_instr_3">On Mac: Open the Passwords app (or System Settings > Passwords), then go to File > Import Passwords and choose this file.</string>
    <string name="csv_instr_4">On iPhone: Go to Settings → Apps → Safari → Import Passwords. Once imported, they will appear in the Passwords app.</string>
